## My suggestion

Instead of overwhelming you with all 90 days at once, we can treat this like a bootcamp.

Every day, you come back and say:

> **"Day 1"**

I'll give you:

* The exact lesson (20–30 minutes)
* The exact coding exercise
* A mini quiz
* Homework
* Solutions if you get stuck
* A small addition to your blood-report app

This way, you'll learn at a steady pace and build the app step by step rather than trying to absorb everything at once.


